{"type": "article", "id": 16039, "title": "黑山羊毛如何变成手工座椅？这位设计师告诉你整个流程", "description": "照这个思路，铲屎官们是不是也可以把家中猫狗的毛搜集起来，做成什么家具？​", "date": "2015-10-14T08:32:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17170, "name": "铲屎官"}, {"id": 17171, "name": "山羊毛"}, {"id": 7891, "name": "手工家具"}, {"id": 5328, "name": "座椅"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605204857tCAJlTIS7a6yvUrW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t女设计师 <a href=\"http://www.behance.net/hannabramford\">Hanna\r\nBramford</a> 是瑞典人，最近她在完成 <a href=\"http://www.lunduniversity.lu.se/international-admissions/bachelors-masters-studies/subject-areas/architecture-and-design\">Lund School\r\nof Architecture</a> 的一个项目：将天然的黑山羊毛制成可坐的椅子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204849HWUEqfNVCID2M3AX.jpg\" title=\"a \" alt=\"a \" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t右上角的女生就是这位设计师了\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052048501CQcmfoYMrqvGLVd.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这就是她最终制成的椅子，椅垫是一团团黑山羊毛制成的\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204850bpn9EDxNdmYSRvAk.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.behance.net/hannabramford\">Hanna Bramford</a> 和一个饲养羊的牧场合作\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204851bZ1TzN3tePC5F2Ww.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">这种羊的品种是 gotland sheep</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204852HRe03bQMwPF7gfU2.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tHanna 手中的羊毛大约重 1.5kg\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204852QfuEIq293ijcwpH8.jpg\" title=\"这一步是去掉羊毛中的结，同时便于清洁羊毛\" alt=\"这一步是去掉羊毛中的结，同时便于清洁羊毛\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>这一步是去掉羊毛中的结，同时给羊毛做清洁</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204853Ud6hTz1p0FQN3PMG.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.61875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t下一步则是将羊毛压缩成圆球了\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204853ejyQrcWdqYMv87bt.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t最终制成的羊毛球有 100 个\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052048548D5Phnpo3yMR9s6H.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t最后一步则是将其组装成椅\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605204856t2jEsN6nXhGP8dve.jpg\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.7421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不知这椅子的寿命有多长时间？感觉趣味性大于实用性啊。照这个思路，铲屎官们是不是也可以把家中猫狗的毛搜集起来，做成什么家具？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/12/this-is-how-hanna-bramfords-black-sheep-stool-was-made/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}